com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class ItemMapping<TItem,TValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.ItemMapping<TItem,TValue>
  • Type Parameters:
    TItem - The type of the items that are mapped.
    TValue - The type of the values the items are mapped to.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContextItemMapping

    public class ItemMapping<TItem,TValue>
extends Object
    Provides different ways to define a mapping from items to values for use with LayoutData.

    Only one of the provided ways to define a mapping can be used at the same time, therefore only one of the properties Mapper, Delegate and Constant should be set on each instance.

    This class supports LayoutData implementations and does not usually have to be used explicitly.
